{"tid":2431422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"發哥領山友看許鞍華紀錄片　周潤發以行動支持香港電影","createTime":"2021-03-03T15:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T02:59:06.000Z","uid":212249,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"727421f9acd11d5a853b25caedc77e35cc923042","tid":2431422,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2891251/chau_thumb_20210303_K_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2891251%2Fchau_thumb_20210303_K_600.jpg&h=c937fbbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年2月，高先電影院（Golden Scene Cinema）在堅尼地城開幕，吸引不少圈中人前往看戲。發哥周潤發昨日（3月2日）帶領跑山隊員鮑起靜、方平、周家怡、莫可欣等一起到高先電影院觀賞有關許鞍華導演的紀錄片《好好拍電影》，力撐香港電影。<br />\n<br />\n《好好拍電影》的導演文念中當日亦有在場，「野生捕獲」發哥當然有一起合照。<br />\n<br />\n《好好拍電影》是著名美術指導文念中首次執導作品，他花了3年時間追訪許鞍華，誠實地展示這位年過70歲的殿堂級女導演在片場內外的不同面貌。<br />\n<br />\n電影由許鞍華讀書年代講到今年73歲的她獲威尼斯影展頒發金獅終身成就獎，這也是獲此殊榮的首位華人女導演。"},{"pid":"ff8fd72bb1473b43cbb38bd766d684ecdfd1418d","tid":2431422,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T15:33:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2891251?r=cpstni\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2891251%3Fr%3Dcpstni&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=970ef52e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2891251?r=cpstni</a>"},{"pid":"57bfa18c120f9e2fc98d95ba8ce08f860b73a698","tid":2431422,"uid":76804,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"仲有人質疑佢唔係黃?<br />\n唔奶共唔做護旗手<br />\n去高登先戲院睇許鞍華d戲"},{"pid":"496a3fa0b023bd73605cb766f36e6c4904655532","tid":2431422,"uid":179409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"57bfa18c120f9e2fc98d95ba8ce08f860b73a698","tid":2431422,"uid":76804,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"仲有人質疑佢唔係黃?<br />\n唔奶共唔做護旗手<br />\n去高登先戲院睇許鞍華d戲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"諗起之前黃秋生對佢嘅評語：<br />\n明明身分地位咁高又大把錢<br />\n完全唔驚封殺<br />\n都驚咗唔敢出聲<br />\n但又要有意無意着黑衫<br />\n做啲嘢出嚟俾人估下佢係咩立場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n低調又唔算<br />\n高調又唔敢"}]}